Come to ClickBus and guarantee your ticket at the best price. Travel with maximum comfort, safety and exclusive discounts.

Board the ClickBus App, the largest online bus ticket sales app in Brazil!

Download the app and start traveling by bus in Brazil. Choose your destination, compare prices between the bus companies and find the best offer for your bus ticket in a simple and secure way, optimized for your phone!

With ClickBus you can find more than 130 bus companies traveling to more than 5,000 destinations.
Choose from: Expresso Guanabara, Viação Cometa, Gontijo, Viação Andorinha, Reunidas Paulista, Viação santa cruz, Águia Branca, Progresso and much more!

Only at ClickBus you have unmissable tickets, travel cheap and even find exclusive discounts to buy your bus ticket to the best destinations in Brazil!
These are unmissable trips for you to enjoy and travel cheap.

EXCLUSIVE ADVANTAGES
◉ 100% secure app.
◉ Purchases in up to 12 installments on credit card.
◉ Bus ticket with up to 60% discount.
◉ Buy your ticket without lining up and without leaving your home.
◉ Find unmissable tickets to the best destinations.
